146
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:11,270
Sekarang sudah musim panas.

147
00:11:14,170 --> 00:11:17,609
Kami memakai lobak muda dan daging. Rasanya enak.

148
00:11:17,839 --> 00:11:19,579
