211
00:16:34,329 --> 00:16:35,900
Ibu si simpanan itu.

212
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,459
Apa?

213
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:39,170
Apa katamu?

214
00:16:39,570 --> 00:16:40,629
Masuk.

215
00:16:40,869 --> 00:16:43,369
Ini hari terakhir dalam hidupmu.

216
